subject: States (US)
lead_paragraph: Erica McKenzie beat Charline Labonte in the sixth round of a shootout, and Jessie Vetter stopped Meghan Agosta to give the United States a 3-2 win over Canada in the Four Nations Cup final in Lake Placid, N.Y.
